CalibrationEnabledToggle.Description: Toggles whether or not calibration is enabled
ContCalibrationToggle.Description: Slowly calibrates to your facial expressions over time
TrackingCalibrateButton.Description: Heighten the influence your expressions make on calibration temporarily
CalibrationInfluenceSlider.Description: Controls how much of an influence your facial expressions have on overall calibration over time
ForceReInitButton.Description: Force VRCFT to unload and reinitialize all modules
ForceRelevancyToggle.Description: Forces sending of all parameters every frame by forcing relevancy
ResetAvatarConfButton.Description: Reset all VRChat OSC config data (will be regenerated when avatar is reloaded)
ResetVRCFTButton.Description: Reset all data stored by VRCFT in your AppData folder
